<placeName cert="high" full="yes">Herakleopolite</placeName></head><div lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="edition"><div n="r" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/><expan>ἔλ<ex cert="high">αβον</ex></expan> <abbr>διω</abbr> <abbr><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">μ</unclear>δ</abbr> <expan><ex cert="high">ἔτους</ex></expan> <num value="7">ζ</num> <expan>Φα<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">με</unclear><ex cert="high">νὼθ</ex></expan> <num value="13">ιγ</num>. 

    <lb n="2"/><handShift new="m2"/> Τρύφων Ἀσκληπιάδηι τῶι ἀδελφῶι χαίρειν 

    <lb n="3"/>καὶ ὑγιαίνειν. λαβὼν τὸ παρὰ σοῦ γράμμα 

    <lb n="4"/>περὶ τῶν κατὰ τοὺς ἐμφανίζοντας τὰ 

    <lb n="5"/>ὑπάρχοντα τοῦ εὐκλήρου ἀδελφοῦ σου 

    <lb n="6"/>ἡμῶν δὲ φίλου γενομένου Πετεχῶντος 

    <lb n="7"/>οὐδὲν σπουδῆς οὐδὲ κακοπαθίας 

    <lb n="8"/>παρέλιπον, ἕως οὗ ἕκαστα ἐπιγνῶ 

    <lb n="9"/>Νεάρχου τοῦ παιδίου ἐπακολουθοῦντος. 

    <lb n="10"/>ἐπεὶ οὖν σὺν θεοῖς οὐδὲν μὲν <expan>προβέβη<ex cert="high">κεν</ex></expan>, 

    <lb n="11"/>ἐξ ἰδίων δὲ γέγονεν ἡ καταρχὴ τοῦ 

    <lb n="12"/>πράγματος χαλκοῦ τριῶν <num value="3"/> <app type="BL"><lem resp="1.99">δαπανη-

    <lb n="13"/>θέντων <gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="character"/><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">η</unclear>θήσεται</lem><rdg>δαπανη<gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="character"/>ε<gap extent="4" reason="illegible" unit="character"/><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">κη</unclear>θήσεται</rdg></app> τὸ πρᾶγμα, ὡς ἂν 

    <lb n="14"/>λάβῃς τὸ γράμμα ἐμβαλοῦ τόν τε ὀρφανὸν 

    <lb n="15"/>καὶ τὴν τούτου μητέρα, ἵνα <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">π</unclear>ρὸς μὲν 

    <lb n="16"/>κατάπληξιν τῶν τολμησάντων ἔχωμεν 

    <lb n="17"/>α<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ὐτο</supplied>ὺς ἑτοίμους πρὸς ἐντυχίαν, πρὸς δὲ 

    <lb n="18"/>λ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ύσ</unclear>ιν αὐτοὶ πάλιν ἐπακολουθήσωσιν 

    <lb n="19"/>τοῖς ὑφ᾽ ἡμῶν οἰκονομηθησομένοις. καὶ 

    <lb n="20"/><choice><corr>σεαυτοῦ</corr><sic>σαυτου</sic></choice> <expan><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ἐπιμ</unclear><ex cert="high">ελοῦ</ex></expan> ἵν᾽ <expan>ὑ<ex cert="high">γιαίνῃς</ex></expan>. 

    <lb n="21"/>ἔρρωσο. <expan><ex cert="high">ἔτους</ex></expan> <num value="7">ζ</num> <expan>Μεχ<ex cert="high">εὶρ</ex></expan> <num value="29">κθ</num>. 
</ab></div><div n="v" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="22"/>τῶι <expan>ἀδελ<ex cert="high">φῶι</ex></expan> Ἀσκληπιάδηι </ab></div></div><div n="meta.18659" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.18659" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="-23" notBefore="-23" type="textDate" value="-0023-02-23">23. Febr. 23 v.Chr.</date></p></div><div n="meta.18659" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="general" type="commentary"><p>Gehört zum Archiv des Reeders Asklepiades. Vgl. Olsson, Papyrusbriefe, Nr. 1-7 und BGU XVI 2665. </p></div><div n="meta.18659" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="mentionedDates" type="commentary"><head>Erwähnte Daten</head><p>Z. 1: <date type="mentioned" value="-0023-03-09">9. März 23 v.Chr.</date></p></div><div n="meta.18659" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl default="NO" subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">BGU</title><biblScope type="volume">4</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">1209</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">18659</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="DDbDP"><series>0001</series>; <biblScope type="volume">4</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">1209</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0001;4;1209" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.18659" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p><bibl default="NO" type="illustration">Schubart, Griechische Paläographie, Abb. 23, S. 47 (Z. 4 - 11)</bibl></p></div><div n="meta.18659" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="translations" type="bibliography"><head>Übersetzungen</head><listBibl default="NO" lang="de"><head lang="de">Deutsch:</head><bibl d